gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Mavericks 148, Hawks 143
gameRecap.excerpt: Luka Doncic scored a career-high 73 points (25-33 FG, 15-16 FT, 8-13 3PT), along with 10 rebounds, and seven assists as the Mavericks defeated the Hawks, 148-143. Trae Young led the Hawks with 30 points and 11 assists in the loss. The Mavericks snap a three-game losing streak to improve to 25-20 as the Hawks move to 18-27.
